  { id: 245, q: "When a notary public takes a 'proof of execution,' they are:", o: ["Witnessing the principal sign the document", "Taking the testimony of a subscribing witness who saw the principal sign", "Checking the document for spelling errors", "Verifying that the document is a true copy"], a: 1 },
